Name: Tiki Brawl
About the game: Grab your friends and throw'em to the sacrifice pit before they throw you! Tiki Brawl is a fast-paced local multiplayer game where players must grab their opponents and throw them into a sacrifice pit to survive and win. Features: Local multiplayer, up to 5 players (4 xinput compatible gamepads + 1 keyboard). Add bots to your matches to make it more challenging! Just one level, but includes lots of randomness with its items: power-ups, weapons, punishments, etc... Try them all! 8-bit sound FX and a catchy Tiki tribal song. (♫ Feed your god, your god is hungry ♫) Highly recommended for parties, with friends, pizza and snacks!
